### Blog System Test

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### Login to get auth token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Create Blog Category
POST {{baseUrl}}/blog/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tutorials",
  "slug": "tutorials",
  "description": "Educational content and tutorials"
}

### Create Blog Tag
POST {{baseUrl}}/blog/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Banking",
  "slug": "banking",
  "description": "Banking related content"
}

### Create Blog Post
POST {{baseUrl}}/blog/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "How to Use Bank Logs Safely",
  "slug": "how-to-use-bank-logs-safely",
  "content": "<h1>Introduction</h1><p>This is a comprehensive guide on how to use bank logs safely and securely.</p>",
  "excerpt": "Learn the best practices for using bank logs safely and securely.",
  "status": "PUBLISHED",
  "isFeatured": true
}

### Get All Blog Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog/posts?page=1&limit=10

### Get Blog Post by Slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog/posts/slug/how-to-use-bank-logs-safely

### Get Blog Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog/categories

### Get Blog Tags
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog/tags

### Get Featured Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog/posts/featured/featured?limit=5

### Search Blog Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog/search?q=bank&page=1&limit=5 